{"tid":2226320,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警漏夜封山 難阻百人登頂  獅子山上顯榮光","createTime":"2020-10-02T03:14:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-02T04:09:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f82c10732594d0628ffde78651ab20da8d4831eb","tid":2226320,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T03:14:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201002/CXMMYMA3Q5BQHIB6HC3N65WSWI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201002%2FCXMMYMA3Q5BQHIB6HC3N65WSWI%2F&d=NeqW8uJC54Uj1%2BY3pyrdAqnpKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=99b5862e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201002%2FCXMMYMA3Q5BQHIB6HC3N65WSWI%2F&h=d9ad1267\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201002/CXMMYMA3Q5BQHIB6HC3N65WSWI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n警漏夜封山 難阻百人登頂 <br />\n獅子山上顯榮光<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】那位國際知名的「 lamentable quisling figure」早上說要無畏無懼，以堅定信心，依法履行維護國家安全的職責。到了下午，數以千計警察在銅鑼灣堵路，任意驅趕、截查、拘捕市民。入夜後，警方更封鎖獅子山，賞月也是罪。玻璃之城，榮光不得歸香港，月光不得照獅山。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：登山者願望：12人盡快返港<br />\n<br />\n記者：潘柏林 羅繼盛<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Ljn7xvM5aek0O4n0mRmyHQfc1S8=/5020x2992/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PAJX6ZXCBZDQNATHMWV65NZS4U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FLjn7xvM5aek0O4n0mRmyHQfc1S8%3D%2F5020x2992%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPAJX6ZXCBZDQNATHMWV65NZS4U.jpg&h=4f6873f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■逾百人昨晚聚集在獅子山頂，並用手機及電筒「光照我城」。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：警全日拘86人 四區議員遭殃  買書也被捕 母女未能團圓<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/PpVtaz2GGxdNs6OccE69GIlRQ9I=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AW26RHTRPRCWRIZL6TSCUJPEFI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FPpVtaz2GGxdNs6OccE69GIlRQ9I%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAW26RHTRPRCWRIZL6TSCUJPEFI.jpg&h=78cf5390&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■有人在山上豎立印有「光復香港 時代革命」的旗幟。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/LyXG6rlRDh3TxuzVDSVcTEHi2dg=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NUHNJUZESBDLJO62GXUJBM56LA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FLyXG6rlRDh3TxuzVDSVcTEHi2dg%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNUHNJUZESBDLJO62GXUJBM56LA.jpg&h=02cf2acc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■大批登山者用手機及電筒照亮獅子山。夏家朗攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「光時」旗隨風飄揚<br />\n<br />\n入夜後，逾十名警員在獅子亭附近山路戒備，並截查行山客，要求搜查背包，有警員警告登山市民，獅子山頂已有過百人，若堅持登山須登記個人資料。<br />\n<br />\n在山頂，日間有最少八位警員駐守在獅子頭，並帶備帳幕和背囊。他們不時透過對講機向上級報告山頂情況，有警員表示現場較難清晰看見，要求增派警員上山增援。至晚上約7時，八名警員撤離山頂。<br />\n<br />\n警員離開後，逾百人聚集於山頂，有登山客以笛子吹奏《願榮光歸香港》，現場山客和應，更高呼「光復香港，時代革命」、「賀佢老母」等口號；亦有人攜同燈籠拍照，並用電筒於「獅頭」和「獅尾」互相輝映。其後更有人在山上豎立一支黑底白字、印有「光復香港 時代革命」的旗幟。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/tFSKDN30Cn6TXNtzZMOmh__qOPE=/1780x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/II6PO4SUN5DSDIY4AZ4EM22QVU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FtFSKDN30Cn6TXNtzZMOmh__qOPE%3D%2F1780x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FII6PO4SUN5DSDIY4AZ4EM22QVU.jpg&h=f7f5fa8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■警方晚上突在慈雲山登山口拉起封鎖線，禁止市民上山及登記落山人士資料。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/biEt1EGXMfW76zQi9-7BL0-pMXQ=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GINPYK4NLFA2NOYSHQYCFCPW6A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FbiEt1EGXMfW76zQi9-7BL0-pMXQ%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGINPYK4NLFA2NOYSHQYCFCPW6A.jpg&h=48b59bdd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■多間傳媒上山採訪，有警員用電筒照射記者。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警：山上疑有非法集結<br />\n<br />\n晚上約9時，警方突在慈雲山登山口拉起封鎖線，離開的市民須登記個人資料，部份行經沙田坳道回家的市民亦遭截查，更須展示住戶證。一名竹園北邨居民因為沒有住戶證，與警員理論，警員指稱山上有人疑涉及非法集結，指令他繞路回家，居民大嘆居住在此40多年，從未遇過這種情況。接近10時，再有兩批東九龍衝鋒隊的防暴警員到場支援，並有多批防暴警察到獅子亭一帶佈防，作雙重截查。<br />\n<br />\n被警方截查後放行的楊小姐稱，昨晚原計劃登獅子山賞月，但卻走錯路上了飛鵝山，折返期間在沙田坳道遭警方截查。警員截查時聲稱「上面有非法集結」，但實際上飛鵝山「鬼影都冇」，完全不明白截查原因。<br />\n<br />\n警方昨全日以大陸公安處理六四死難家屬掃墓的手法嚴限市民登山，網民稱中秋清晨已有六名警員在山頂駐守，拍攝照片的facebook專頁「山瘋Hill We Go」版主稱，昨早約7時與友人從「獅尾」位置登頂，在山上閱讀《蘋果日報》、吃月餅和拍照，發現「獅頭」位置有穿反光衣的人疑似用望遠鏡觀察他們，後來他們走近才發現是警察，更有多種顏色的旗袋放在地上。"},{"pid":"ba76187ba6a0b00a70371d76ab6140dfed574705","tid":2226320,"uid":151196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T03:14:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ce8537916d9ff5961dca439d2592f6a9171bbd0","tid":2226320,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T03:17:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e5bf9dd79563cd6bf1d6957140834cd1b290a482","tid":2226320,"uid":158888,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T03:24:14.000Z","msg":"感謝各位手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8f65626dc072b34cb4cfa56c61231ce0dcf64f7","tid":2226320,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e5bf9dd79563cd6bf1d6957140834cd1b290a482","tid":2226320,"uid":158888,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T03:24:14.000Z","msg":"感謝各位手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T03:25:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d155805a12cf38ef233a57eff119ed4d62056ef6","tid":2226320,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T03:25:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5e624416dc50e91ad773caa6d2ed13a4730c182","tid":2226320,"uid":221171,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T03:25:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rZwDGbu.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrZwDGbu.gif&h=d8b83b36&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"383a92f66812df00158ee17231b8ce67872929a2","tid":2226320,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T03:42:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5111c7e5b751471a2557559be876cacbd5ac715b","tid":2226320,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci